translation[5]{c,v,t}:
  28,1,Taa seen Meem
  28,2,Yeh kitaab e mubeen(clear book) ki aayat hain
  28,3,Hum Moosa aur Firoun ka kuch haal theek theek tumhein sunate hain aisey logon ke faiyde ke liye jo iman layein
  28,4,"Waqia yeh hai ke Firoun ne zameen mein sarkashi ki aur uske bashindon ko girohon mein taseem kardiya, un mein se ek giroh ko woh zaleel karta tha, iske ladkon ko qatal karta aur uski ladkiyon ko jeeta (zinda) rehne deta tha. Fil waqai woh mufsid (mischief-makers) logon mein se tha"
  28,5,"Aur hum yeh irada rakhte thay ke meharbani karein un logon par jo zameen mein zaleel karke rakkhey gaye thay, aur unhein peshwa(leaders) bana dein, aur unhi ko waris banayein"